rts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Guns+N%27+Roses|archivedate=March 9, 2014}}</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:3em;font-size:75%\"|[[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br><ref name=swi>{{cite web|url=http://swisscharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Guns+N%27+Roses|title=Swiss Charts > Guns N' Roses|publisher=swisscharts.com Hung Medien|accessdate=December 7, 2008|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080218100441/http://swisscharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Guns+N%27+Roses|archivedate=February 18, 2008}}</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:3em;font-size:75%\"|[[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=uk>{{cite web|url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/artist/_/guns%20n%27%20roses/|title=UK Charts > Guns N' Roses|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=April 12, 2010|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120912154736/http://www.theofficialcharts.com/artist/_/guns%20n'%20roses/|archivedate=September 12, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2008\n|align=\"left\"| \"[[Chinese Democracy (song)|Chinese Democracy]]\"\n| 34\n| 5\n| 54\n| 26\n| 38\n| 3\n| 15\n| 27\n| 3\n| 11\n| 27\n|-\n|align=\"left\"| \"[[Better (Guns N' Roses song)|Better]]\"\n| \u2014\n| 18\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n|-\n|2009\n|align=\"left\"| \"[[Street of Dreams (Guns N' Roses song)|Street of Dreams]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n| *\n|-\n| colspan=\"13\" style=\"font-size:8pt;\"| \"\u2013\" denotes releases that did not chart. * denotes promotional release; not eligible for international charts\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n===Footnotes===\n{{notelist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n*[http://www.gnrevolution.com/viewtopic.php?id=5059 Chinese Whispers \u2013 The Secret History of the New Studio Album]\n*[https://www.loudersound.com/features/guns-n-roses-the-making-of-chinese-democracy Classic Rock Magazine: The Making of Chinese Democracy]\n*[https://www.nytimes.com/2005/03/06/arts/music/the-most-expensive-album-never-made.html